#. Tag: title
#: flowcode.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "&flowcode;"
msgstr "&flowcode;"

#. Tag: title
#: flowcode.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&flowcode; allows for very quick and easy construction of a PIC program. "
"After the user has constructed a flowchart from the program parts available, "
"&ktechlab; can then convert the flowchart into a number of formats. To "
"output hex, for example, the following chain of conversions takes place:"
msgstr ""
"&flowcode; omogoča zelo hitro in enostavno izdelavo programa PIC. Ko "
"uporabnik sestavi diagram poteka iz delov programa, ki so na voljo, "
"&ktechlab; lahko nato pretvori diagram poteka v več formatov. Za izpis "
"šestnajstiškega na primer poteka naslednja veriga pretvorb:"

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &flowcode; is converted to &microbe;; a high-level language whose "
"compiler is distributed with &ktechlab;."
msgstr ""
"&flowcode; se pretvori v &microbe;; visoko-nivojski jezik, katerega "
"prevajalnik se distribuira skupaj z &ktechlab;."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <command>microbe</command> executable then compiles the &microbe; file "
"to PIC assembly."
msgstr ""
"Izvršljiva datoteka <command>microbe</command> nato prevede &microbe; "
"datoteke v zbirnik PIC."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, <command>gpasm</command> takes the PIC assembly file, and outputs "
"the hex for the program."
msgstr ""
"Končno <command>gpasm</command> vzame datoteko zbirnika PIC in naredi "
"šestnajstiški izhodni program."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course, if you don't have gputils installed - with which <command>gpasm</"
"command> is distributed - then the last step can't be performed."
msgstr ""
"Seveda, če nimate nameščenega programa gputils - s katerimi se "
"<command>gpasm</command> distribuira - potem zadnjega koraka ni mogoče "
"izvesti."

#. Tag: title
#: flowcode.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Program"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje programa"

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every &flowcode; program needs a unique starting point - this is the place "
"where your program will be run from on PIC startup. To define this point, "
"open up the FlowParts sidebar on the left, and drag across the "
"<guilabel>Start</guilabel> part. &ktechlab; will only allow you to use one "
"of these."
msgstr ""
"Vsak &flowcode; program potrebuje edinstveno izhodišče - to je mesto, od "
"koder se bo vaš program zagnal ob zagonu PIC. Če želite definirati to točko, "
"odprite stransko vrstico FlowParts na levi in povlecite čez del "
"<guilabel>Začetek</guilabel>. &ktechlab; vam bo omogočil uporabo le enega od "
"teh."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then construct your program by using the predefined parts on the "
"left - or insert code of your own (in assembly or &microbe; format) via the "
"<guilabel>Embed</guilabel> part. The flow of the program is controlled via "
"the connections between the FlowParts - <xref linkend=\"connecting_components"
"\"/> offers more detail on creating connections."
msgstr ""
"Nato lahko sestavite svoj program z uporabo vnaprej določenih delov na levi "
"- ali vstavite svojo kodo (v obliki zbirnika ali &microbe;) prek dela "
"<guilabel>Vdelaj</guilabel>. Tok programa je nadzorovan prek povezav med "
"FlowParts - <xref linkend=\"connecting_components\"/> ponuja več podrobnosti "
"o ustvarjanju povezav."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&flowcode; imposes limitations in addition to those of circuits on what can "
"be connected. For example, each FlowPart can only have one output "
"connection. Additional limitations are described in <xref linkend="
"\"nestling_flowcode\"/>."
msgstr ""
"&flowcode; nalaga omejitve poleg omejitev vezij glede tega, kaj je mogoče "
"povezati. Na primer, vsak FlowPart ima lahko samo eno izhodno povezavo. "
"Dodatne omejitve so opisane v <xref linkend=\"nestling_flowcode\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: flowcode.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "PIC Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve PIC"

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you create a new &flowcode; document, you'll notice a picture of the "
"PIC you're using in the top-left corner of the work area. This represents "
"the initial settings of the PIC."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite nov &flowcode; dokument, boste v zgornjem levem kotu delovnega "
"območja opazili sliko PIC-a, ki ga uporabljate. To predstavlja začetne "
"nastavitve PIC."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each pin shown on the picture of the PIC shows the initial type of pin "
"(input or output), and its initial state (high or low). You can change these "
"by dragging the pin to set the type, and clicking on it to toggle its state."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka nogica, prikazana na sliki PIC-a, prikazuje začetni tip nogice (vhod "
"ali izhod) in njeno začetno stanje (visoko ali nizko). Te lahko spremenite "
"tako, da povlečete nogico, da ji nastavite vrsto, in kliknete nanjo, da "
"preklopite njeno stanje."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Settings</guilabel> dialog, invoked by clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Settings</guibutton> button, also allows you to edit the initial "
"pin types and states - in this case, by editing the binary values written to "
"the PORT and TRIS registers. As well as pin settings though, the dialog "
"allows editing of the initial values of variables in the PIC program."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Nastavitve</guilabel>, ki ga prikličete s klikom na "
"gumb <guibutton>Nastavitve</guibutton>, omogoča tudi urejanje začetnih tipov "
"in stanj nogic - v tem primeru z urejanjem binarnih vrednosti, zapisanih v "
"registrih PORT in TRIS. Pogovorno okno poleg nastavitev nogic omogoča tudi "
"urejanje začetnih vrednosti spremenljivk v programu PIC."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom, there is a list of currently defined pin maps, as well as "
"buttons to manipulate them. Pin maps are used to specify how a seven segment "
"or a keypad is connected to a PIC. To use the <guilabel>Seven Segment</"
"guilabel> or the <guilabel>Keypad</guilabel> &flowcode; parts, you will need "
"to define a pin map here first."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu je seznam trenutno definiranih map nogic in gumbov za upravljanje z "
"njimi. Mape nogic se uporabljajo za določitev, kako je sedem segmentov ali "
"tipkovnica povezana s PIC. Za uporabo <guilabel>Sedem segmentov</guilabel> "
"ali delov <guilabel>Tipkovnice</guilabel> &flowcode;, boste morali tukaj "
"najprej definirati mapo nogic."

#. Tag: title
#: flowcode.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nestling &flowcode;"
msgstr "Gnezdenje &flowcode;"

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many FlowParts, such as subroutines and loops, can contain code of their "
"own. After creating such a container, FlowParts can be added by either "
"dragging or dropping them into the container. The container will be "
"highlighted to indicate that it will become the new parent of the FlowPart."
msgstr ""
"Mnogi FlowParts, kot so podprogrami in zanke, lahko vsebujejo lastno kodo. "
"Ko ustvarite tak vsebnik, lahko FlowParts dodate tako, da jih povlečete ali "
"spustite v vsebnik. Vsebnik bo označen, kar pomeni, da bo postal novi "
"nadrejeni element FlowPart."

#. Tag: para
#: flowcode.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The container takes responsibility for FlowParts nestled inside. If the "
"expand button is unclicked, all contained FlowParts will be hidden - and "
"likewise, the contents will be shown when the expand button is clicked "
"again. Connections cannot be made between FlowParts in different containers, "
"and the contents of a container will be moved about along with the container."
msgstr ""
"Vsebnik prevzame odgovornost za FlowParts, ki so nameščeni v njem. Če gumba "
"za razširitev ne kliknete, bodo vsi vsebovani FlowParts skriti - in prav "
"tako bo vsebina prikazana, ko znova kliknete gumb za razširitev. Med "
"FlowParts v različnih vsebnikih ni mogoče vzpostaviti povezav, vsebina "
"vsebnika pa se bo premikala skupaj z vsebnikom."
